\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 No people.\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  His mother reminded him, placing a hand firmly on his head.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab Peter\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s ears was burning.  What rhymes with shorts?}
